column23: data exclusion stategy (value=1, ignore specific hours; value=2, ignore all data before the first midnight and after the last midnight)
column24: n hours ignored at start of meas (if strategy=1)
column25: n hours ignored at end of meas (if strategy=1)
column26: n days of measurement after which all data is ignored (if strategy=1)
column27: epoch size to which acceleration was averaged (seconds)

column15: recalibration attempted with all available data, but possibly not good enough: Check calibration error variable to varify this
